reviewText: Very enjoyable.  Gave a good bit of detail about the airplanes and the flights.

Excellent BlueRay of both aircrafts (Boeing 787 Dreamliner and Embraer 190), covers all activities, from flight programming, taxing, depart, cockpit explanation, cruise flight and landing.
Clear explanations, Camera views from different angles.

This is another Justplanes superior product.
